1. Da li *dolazite* na rođendansku proslavu? (Are you coming to the birthday party?)
2. *Dolazite* li često u ovaj restoran? (Do you come to this restaurant often?)
3. Upravo *dolazite* u pravo vreme. (You are coming at the right time.)
4. Kada *dolazite* u Beograd? (When are you coming to Belgrade?)
5. *Dolazite* li sami ili sa prijateljima? (Are you coming alone or with friends?)
6. Žao mi je, ali ne *dolazite* u obzir za ovaj posao. (I'm sorry, but you are not being considered for this job.)
7. Nisam siguran da li *dolazite* u subotu ili u nedelju. (I'm not sure if you are coming on Saturday or Sunday.)
8. Moramo se pobrinuti da *dolazite* na vreme. (We need to make sure that you come on time.)
9. *Dolazite* li pešice ili taksijem? (Are you coming on foot or by taxi?)
10. Kada biste *dolazili* u posetu? (When would you come to visit?)